CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 1, 1947, pg. 26, reads: "All Aboard for D. C.  - The Centre YMCA swimming team who will go to Washington, D. C. to engage in a dual meet with Howard University Saturday. Left to right, standing: Coach Fountain, Oscar Kinderson, Alfred Hooe, Terence Garmon, Samual Guyton, Primo Omogrosso, William Ashley and William Seay. Seated, left to right: James Lewis, Samuel Lawler, William Jones, Nathaneal Washington and Reginald Garmon. - Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Centre Avenue YMCA swimming team with coach Fountain on left, and standing: Oscar Kinderson, Alfred Hooe, Terence Garmon, Samual or Samuel Guyton, Primo Omogrosso, William Ashley, William Seay; seated: James Lewis, Samuel Lawler, William Jones, Nathaneal Washington and Reginald Garmon posed in YMCA pool
